---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About the Epstein Files Tracker"
  description="An independent, source-first tracker of the Epstein Files. Every claim cited, every name cross-referenced, every document linked. How and why this project exists."
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-6">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ name: 'About', href: '/about' }]} />
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-[2.75rem] font-serif font-bold leading-[1.15] mb-4">
        About the Epstein Files Tracker
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        An independent, source-first tracker of the Epstein Files. Every claim cited, every name cross-referenced, every document linked.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10">
    <div class="prose-article">
      <h2>What Is This?</h2>
      <p>
        The Epstein Transparency Project tracks every development around the
        Epstein Files and the Epstein Transparency Act. We present the facts
        in a clear, organized format so the public can follow this story without
        wading through noise.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Source-first.</strong> Every piece on this site links directly
        to its original source. We believe in full attribution â€” readers should
        always be able to verify what they read.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>People database.</strong> We maintain profiles of individuals named in
        the documents, along with officials, associates, and other connected parties.
        Each profile is cross-referenced with all related coverage.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Timeline.</strong> A chronological record of key events in the case,
        from the earliest allegations through the latest document releases and legislative action.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Continuous updates.</strong> We track the latest developments as they
        happen, so you don't have to piece the story together yourself.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        This site presents publicly available information from established reporting
        and public records. Inclusion of any individual in the people database does not
        imply guilt or wrongdoing.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For corrections, takedown requests, or other inquiries, please reach out
        via email at
        <a href="mailto:contact@epsteintransparencyact.com">contact@epsteintransparencyact.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
